{"tid":1312514,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"以下係我係公立醫院病房聽到既野","createTime":"2019-07-13T14:02:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T14:39:55.000Z","uid":112700,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d389bc436d88a861e66f741302f4c19c3a938adc","tid":1312514,"uid":112700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T14:02:33.000Z","msg":"聽到APN比成班RN既指引，淨係聽到幾句。<br />\n<br />\n1:<br />\n醫護人員問起傷口時，病人有權拒絕透露傷口形成的原因。除非病人承認傷口來自槍械/布袋彈，醫護人員才需要上報，否則亦毋須深究。<br />\n<br />\n2:<br />\n病人入院時可要求院方拒絕批露任何病人私隱，會有相應措施提供，小至拒絕作答某病人是否住院/鎖起牌板etc<br />\n<br />\n3:<br />\n當有警察來到病房，要與某病人「傾下謁」，院方不會要求醫護人員拒權警察進入病房，惟醫護人員必須檢查委任證。<br />\n<br />\n好過分囉，垃圾HA包庇暴徒<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">隱瞞傷口來源</span></span></strong>，處處維護暴徒，比佢地<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">向院方要求隱瞞病人資訊</span></span></strong>，可恥！"},{"pid":"1a7c2bdd953403be88b461e2d577a32ad8db2d48","tid":1312514,"uid":112700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T14:03:09.000Z","msg":"推比大家睇下HA有幾可恥"},{"pid":"472b1ff850e5b1293a5ed0a7a383e63b113f355b","tid":1312514,"uid":112700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T14:05:09.000Z","msg":"繼續推比大家睇下HA有幾可恥"},{"pid":"c919ae7147c59a89d2ff67edf5f776bfbedffb04","tid":1312514,"uid":112700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T14:05:34.000Z","msg":"繼續推比大家睇下HA有幾可恥"},{"pid":"e5041c6d1d8da0e040b730dd8d77fecc90fb078f","tid":1312514,"uid":112700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T14:06:07.000Z","msg":"繼續推比大家睇下HA有幾可恥"},{"pid":"99770fbeec546e3cad5866015dd25bd86287ce06","tid":1312514,"uid":112700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T14:07:28.000Z","msg":"繼續推比大家睇下HA有幾可恥"},{"pid":"2c2626aa53c8062b78b52c1166b6f8577f65fedd","tid":1312514,"uid":112700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T14:07:56.000Z","msg":"繼續推比大家睇下HA有幾可恥"},{"pid":"0e0cdc7dd